{"tid":168188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本學校新型廁所「中間放一張桌子」網友疑惑到底是做什麼用的","createTime":"2017-03-23T11:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T14:58:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"293a54c2ba9e64031d2915abc338183f7f31d707","tid":168188,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"在日本動漫中，經常經常可以看到邊緣人在廁所吃便當的場景。近日有日本網友PO文，表示最近日本有些學校導入了新型的廁所，不僅有單間，中間還有個桌子，立刻引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170322/1490155067764932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20170322%2F1490155067764932.jpg&h=4a5c9c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友在2ch論壇上展開討論，紛紛留言「看起來不會有欺凌了」、「可以跟朋友一起吃飯了」、「現在的孩子太幸運了！」、「站到上面可以看到別人拉屎」 、「反而不方便去上廁所了」、「桌子是用來吃廁飯的」、「更容易拿桶裝水澆別人了」、「有桌子可以解鎖更多xx姿勢」」、「真心想問桌子拿來做什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170322/1490155078814149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20170322%2F1490155078814149.jpg&h=dc07fe5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以到底為什麼廁所裡面要放一個桌子呢？據日媒報導，廁所經常給人骯髒黑暗的印象，如今越來越多的學校開始歐美化，為了讓廁所能夠讓人感覺陽光整潔，所以加入了各種裝飾，而桌子就是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n原來這個桌子就是為了讓廁所看起來陽光的裝飾哦，這理由真的是讓人失語又無法反駁......分享出去，讓大家看到吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fullyu.com/article/10425/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E6%94%BE%E6%A1%8C%E5%AD%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Farticle%2F10425%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A1%258C%25E5%25AD%2590%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c9d5185a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fullyu.com/article/10425/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E6%94%BE%E6%A1%8C%E5%AD%90/</a>"},{"pid":"be62eac82e8c371a395da7447ea3c7e2851b4573","tid":168188,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"有啲大廣場都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇標題仲以為廁格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3740b7171db18b473c191d3d2f9ad441b683a6ee","tid":168188,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"賭錢"},{"pid":"d34be664726a256532cd8237b1312d848640d586","tid":168188,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3aec83609b1e0397473294d9aa7c75031ef6c818","tid":168188,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"拖條女過黎比十幾個人圍住黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ffc2ef25c50544e34745beb75afddb9fbb6135","tid":168188,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01ec51e384a07a3dc41dc21524991a58acfa176","tid":168188,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"日本學校新型廁所 = 香港超豪華商場新型廁所 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}